                    {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 2,
                        "content": "Installatie Handleiding",
                        "level": 1
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 3,
                        "content": "Volg deze stappen om IntraVox te installeren op uw Nextcloud server. De installatie duurt ongeveer 5 minuten."
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "columns": 1,
                "backgroundColor": "",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 1,
                        "content": "Vereisten",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 2,
                        "content": "Voordat u begint, controleer of uw server voldoet aan de volgende eisen:\n\n| Component | Minimum | Aanbevolen |\n|-----------|---------|------------|\n| Nextcloud | 27.0 | 28.0+ |\n| PHP | 8.0 | 8.2+ |\n| Database | MySQL 8.0 | MariaDB 10.6+ |\n| Geheugen | 256 MB | 512 MB+ |"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "columns": 1,
                "backgroundColor": "var(--color-background-hover)",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 1,
                        "content": "Stap 1: Download",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 2,
                        "content": "Download IntraVox via de Nextcloud App Store of handmatig:\n\n**Via App Store (aanbevolen):**\n1. Ga naar Nextcloud Admin > Apps\n2. Zoek naar \"IntraVox\"\n3. Klik op \"Download en activeer\"\n\n**Handmatig:**\n```bash\ncd /var/www/nextcloud/apps\nwget https://github.com/intravox/releases/latest.tar.gz\ntar -xzf latest.tar.gz\n```"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "columns": 1,
                "backgroundColor": "",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 1,
                        "content": "Stap 2: Activeren",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 2,
                        "content": "Activeer de app via de command line:\n\n```bash\nsudo -u www-data php occ app:enable intravox\n```\n\nOf via de web interface:\n1. Ga naar Settings > Apps\n2. Zoek IntraVox in de lijst\n3. Klik op \"Enable\""
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "columns": 1,
                "backgroundColor": "var(--color-background-hover)",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 1,
                        "content": "Stap 3: Configuratie",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 2,
                        "content": "Voer de setup wizard uit:\n\n```bash\nsudo -u www-data php occ intravox:setup\n```\n\nDit creëert:\n- De IntraVox groupfolder\n- Standaard homepage\n- Navigatie structuur\n- Initiële configuratie"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "columns": 1,
                "backgroundColor": "",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 1,
                        "content": "Stap 4: Gebruikers Toevoegen",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 2,
                        "content": "Voeg gebruikers toe aan de IntraVox group:\n\n1. Ga naar Users > Groups\n2. Selecteer \"IntraVox Users\" of \"IntraVox Editors\"\n3. Voeg de gewenste gebruikers toe\n\n**Rollen:**\n- **Users**: Alleen lezen\n- **Editors**: Lezen en bewerken\n- **Admins**: Volledige controle"
                    }
                ]
            },
